name: The Last Dino (imohamed7)
description:
Around 65.5 million years ago a mass extinction happened in earth which wiped out all the dino lived happily and by luck one dino survived which is still in danger.

Help poor dino to survive as long as possible from meteorite strikes.

Please type your high score in comment section. let see how long you can survive.

All the assets used are created by me except sound which i downloaded from free sound website.

This game is submitted for weekly game jam.

Thank you for spending time in this game.
